:cypress-spin: *Cypress on-call summary for 4/7-4/11*:cypress-spin:
• :white_check_mark: fixed Cypress CI occasionally failing (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69616) to to different browser versions across parallel runs
• :white_check_mark: fixed slowdown (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69603) caused by old workspace datasources not being cleaned up after a test run
• :white_check_mark: `edit-existing-app` was failing due to long version history causing 414s & slowdowns. Fixed by deleting old app versions & updating test to do the same (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/69760).
